org.hibernate.ogm.datastore.couchdb.dialect.backend.json.designdocument.impl

Class DesignDocument

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hibernate.ogm.datastore.couchdb.dialect.backend.json.impl.Document
      • org.hibernate.ogm.datastore.couchdb.dialect.backend.json.designdocument.impl.DesignDocument
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    TuplesDesignDocument

    public class DesignDocument
extends Document
    Represents a CouchDB design document. Design documents are special CouchDB documents containing application logic in form of JavaScript, more specifically views (which apply map/reduce routines) and lists (which render other documents or views).
    Author:
    Andrea Boriero <dreborier@gmail.com>, Gunnar Morling
